Recreated migrations file due to change filed `terminated_at` to `date_terminated` in JobResult model.
Changed job result log level to FAILURE from INFO in revoke flow.
Changed `job_label.html`. Added handling for all other current JobResultStatusChoices values.
Changed `render_jobresult_status`. Added handling for all other current JobResultStatusChoices values.
`Result Data` in `Summary of Result` panel on JobResult detail view is only rendered when job result status is SUCCESS.
`Duration` in `Summary of Result` panel on JobResult detail view is only rendered when `date_done` and `date_started` are set.
